item.title: Journal
item.description: I can’t gather when it started, but for the longest time living has felt like a major chore. And quite frankly sometimes you don’t quite feel like doing a chore anymore. No matter how hard I try, I can’t seem to find the sense of joy in this unceasinsg journey. My one realizatioin is that I deeply enjoy being good at something and sharing this talent with others.
